jalse.listeners

Class EntityAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • jalse.listeners.EntityAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EntityListener

    public abstract class EntityAdapter
extends java.lang.Object
implements EntityListener
    An abstract adapter for EntityListener. This is a convenience class for creating entity listeners that may not require a full implementation. All methods implemented by this class are empty.
    Author:
    Elliot Ford
